{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Why Do We Even Need Promises?",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Let’s start with the real problem.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Imagine this:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "const data = fetch(\"https://api.example.com\");\nconsole.log(data);\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "You expect data.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "But what you get is… not data.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Why?",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Because fetching data takes time.",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "text": "JavaScript doesn’t pause and wait—it keeps going.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Without a system to handle “future results,” things break quickly.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "That system is called a ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "Promise",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "What Is a Promise? (Very Simple Explanation)",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "A Promise is:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "“A placeholder for a value that will exist later.”",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Think of it like ordering food:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "You place the order",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "You get a receipt (Promise)",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "The food comes later",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "The receipt isn’t the food—but it guarantees something is coming.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "The Three States of a Promise",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "A Promise can only be in one of three states:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "type": null,
        "start": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Pending",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " → Still waiting",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Fulfilled",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " → Successfully completed",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Rejected",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " → Something went wrong",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Think of it like this:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Pending → Cooking",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Fulfilled → Served",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Rejected → Burned",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "No fourth option.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Creating a Basic Promise",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Here’s the simplest example:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "const myPromise = new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n  setTimeout(() => {\n    resolve(\"Done!\");\n  }, 2000);\n});\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "What’s happening here?",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "We create a Promise",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "It waits 2 seconds",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Then it calls ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "resolve()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "The result becomes available later.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Consuming a Promise with ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": ".then()",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "A Promise by itself doesn’t show results.",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "type": "hardBreak"
        },
        {
          "text": "You attach handlers.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "myPromise.then((result) => {\n  console.log(result);\n});\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Output after 2 seconds:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Done!\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": ".then()",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " runs only when the Promise is fulfilled.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Handling Errors with ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": ".catch()",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "What if something fails?",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "const myPromise = new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n  reject(\"Something went wrong\");\n});\n\nmyPromise\n  .then((result) => console.log(result))\n  .catch((error) => console.log(error));\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Output:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": null
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Something went wrong\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": ".catch()",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " handles rejected Promises.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Why Promises Are Better Than Callbacks",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Before Promises, we had callbacks.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Example:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "getData(function(result) {\n  processData(function(processed) {\n    saveData(function(saved) {\n      console.log(saved);\n    });\n  });\n});\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "This is called ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "callback hell",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Promises flatten this structure:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "getData()\n  .then(processData)\n  .then(saveData)\n  .then(console.log)\n  .catch(console.error);\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Cleaner. More readable. More maintainable.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Real-World Example: Fetching Data",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Most modern APIs return Promises.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "fetch(\"https://api.example.com/users\")\n  .then((response) => response.json())\n  .then((data) => console.log(data))\n  .catch((error) => console.log(error));\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "What’s happening:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "type": null,
        "start": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "fetch()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " returns a Promise",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "First ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".then()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " converts response to JSON",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Second ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".then()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " handles the data",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": ".catch()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " handles errors",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "This pattern is everywhere in modern JavaScript.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Visual Flow of a Promise",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "alt": "Image",
        "src": "https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise/promises.png",
        "title": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "attrs": {
        "alt": "Image",
        "src": "https://media2.dev.to/dynamic/image/width%3D800%2Cheight%3D%2Cfit%3Dscale-down%2Cgravity%3Dauto%2Cformat%3Dauto/https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Ft24c294i6z6l5bseuqo1.png",
        "title": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Flow:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "attrs": {
        "type": null,
        "start": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Promise created",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Pending",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Fulfilled OR Rejected",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": ".then()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " or ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".catch()",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " executes",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Simple lifecycle. Predictable behavior.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Promise Chaining",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Promises can be chained because ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": ".then()",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " returns a new Promise.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "doSomething()\n  .then((result) => {\n    return result + \" Next step\";\n  })\n  .then((finalResult) => {\n    console.log(finalResult);\n  });\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Each step waits for the previous one to complete.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "This creates a clean flow of asynchronous logic.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontalRule"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Introducing ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "async",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " / ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "await",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " (Quick Mention)",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Modern JavaScript lets you write Promises like synchronous code:",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "js"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "async function getData() {\n  try {\n    const response = await fetch(\"https://api.example.com\");\n    const data = await response.json();\n    console.log(data);\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.log(error);\n  }\n}\n",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
